WEBVTT

00:03.672 --> 00:05.950
You only ever knew him as the man
you wanted him to be.

00:05.951 --> 00:07.399
You only knew him as a boy!

00:07.400 --> 00:08.779
You made sure of that.

00:08.780 --> 00:12.067
We want you home,
we're both worried sick.

00:12.068 --> 00:13.432
Just come home.

00:13.485 --> 00:14.892
I took the story to Caden.

00:14.893 --> 00:16.172
You know what he says?

00:16.172 --> 00:18.348
"It was a robbery gone wrong."

00:18.349 --> 00:20.908
Any newspapers use your services?

00:20.909 --> 00:23.340
Your son will face significant
challenges.

00:23.341 --> 00:25.708
They might be aggressive
when they were gentle,

00:25.709 --> 00:28.076
indiscreet when they were tactful.

00:28.077 --> 00:31.596
And without this filter,
every thought can become a speech.

00:31.597 --> 00:33.688
I did... your... phone.

00:36.845 --> 00:37.868
Caden, what, is it?

00:37.869 --> 00:38.869
Help!

00:39.277 --> 00:40.277
Help!

00:40.301 --> 00:41.483
Caden, Caden!

00:43.373 --> 00:47.283
This programme contains
very strong language

